# Adding anchor peers to the channel

## Step 1: Fetch the latest config block from the channel

## Step 2: Edit the config and prepare the pb file for transaction

`https://hyperledger-fabric.readthedocs.io/en/release-2.2/create_channel/create_channel.html?highlight=anchor%20peer%20update#set-anchor-peers`

`configtxgen -outputAnchorPeersUpdate anchor_peer_tx.pb -profile AgeOfUltronChannel -asOrg Hulk -channelID ageofultron -configPath ./`

`configtxgen -outputAnchorPeersUpdate anchor_peer_tx_i.pb -profile AgeOfUltronChannel -asOrg Ironman -channelID ageofultron -configPath ./`

`peer channel update -f anchor_peer_tx.pb -c ageofultron -o orderer.bx.com:7050 --tls --cafile "${ORDERER_TLS_CA}"`

`peer channel update -f anchor_peer_tx_i.pb -c ageofultron -o orderer.bx.com:7050 --tls --cafile "${ORDERER_TLS_CA}"`